{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And most of those who managed to survive, who had such an instinct of survival that they could survive for four or five years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they came there when they were 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in these conditions they could survive, they were completely dehumanized.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was a terrible thing to-- to see them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But at the same time, they were so dehumanized that they really were absolutely vicious to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were really very, very bad-- bad the way they treated us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had that already when we arrived on the ramp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had that already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That it was quite obvious they were very jealous of us that we still were well-fed, well-dressed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they were already completely gone, I mean, and had so many terrible years behind them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And at that time, I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Later on, I understood it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I mean, I-- I found it-- I mean, I understood what has happened and how dehumanized they became.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because they had such a strong instinct of survival.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And sadly, there were many who, I mean, most-- most good people-- no, no, I shouldn't say good people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That's wrong, the wrong expression when I say good people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Many many didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I mean, most people didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But those who survived, they had to have such an instinct of survival.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That at that point, very many, most of them, would compromise already and would be willing to do, really, anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they had to be in this position that they-- they were-- they could replace the SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They had to show that they are worse than the SS, just to prove it, which was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And as I say, at the time, I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
